                <p>使用天然的食材，完美詮釋蛋糕口感</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 wow fadeInDown" data-wow-duration="1000ms" data-wow-delay="900ms">
                <img src="~/Company/Company/images/coffeebean.jpg" />
                <h3>FRESH</h3>
                <p>專業咖啡烘焙，享受優質體驗</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
